WEBVTT

00:11:57.673 --> 00:12:00.962
rrezikun per atak ne zemer apo
hipertension.

00:12:01.701 --> 00:12:02.961
Ju mund te pyesni:

00:12:03.472 --> 00:12:08.953
A mund ta perdorim per te zbuluar
emocionet e politikaneve?

00:12:08.977 --> 00:12:10.517
(Te qeshura)

00:12:10.541 --> 00:12:12.395
Per shembull, gjate nje debati.

00:12:13.220 --> 00:12:14.673
Pergjigja eshte po.

00:12:15.167 --> 00:12:17.111
Duke perdorur rregjistrimet televizive,

00:12:17.135 --> 00:12:21.181
ne mund te dallojme rrahjet e zemres
se politikaneve,

00:12:21.205 --> 00:12:23.251
gjendjen shpirterore dhe stresin,

00:12:23.275 --> 00:12:26.853
dhe mbase ne te ardhmen nese
po na genjejne apo jo.

00:12:27.495 --> 00:12:30.491
Mund ta perdorim ne kerkimet
ne marketing,